### ChatClientAgentRunOptions

Specialized run options for individual invocations.

```csharp
public class ChatClientAgentRunOptions : AgentRunOptions
{
    // Constructor
    public ChatClientAgentRunOptions(ChatOptions? chatOptions = null)

    // Per-invocation chat configuration
    public ChatOptions? ChatOptions { get; set; }
        // Merged with agent's default chat options
        // Run options take precedence for specific settings
        // Collections (like Tools) are unioned

    // Custom chat client for this invocation
    public Func<IChatClient, IChatClient>? ChatClientFactory { get; set; }
        // Factory to decorate/replace chat client on per-request basis
        // Receives agent's configured client, returns potentially modified client

    // Clone method
    public ChatClientAgentRunOptions Clone()
}
```

